"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The sns.lmplot function is a figure-level function that combines regplot() and FacetGrid. It should not be used within a FacetGrid. Instead, use the regplot function within the FacetGrid, or use lmplot directly without creating a FacetGrid.\", \"patch\": \"5,6c5\\n< g = sns.FacetGrid(data=tips, col='time', row='sex')\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> sns.lmplot(data=tips, x='total_bill', y='tip', col='time', row='sex')\\n\"}"